{"word":"Threshing","slug":"threshing","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Threshing</b> by beating<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=17'>Rth 2:17</a><br/> by treading<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=4'>Deu 25:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=25&verse=10'>Isa 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=11'>Hos 10:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=9'>1Co 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=18'>1Ti 5:18</a><br/> With instruments:<br/> - Of wood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=22'>2Sa 24:22</a> <br/> - Of iron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=3'>Amo 1:3</a> <br/> - A cart wheel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=28'>Isa 28:28</a> <br/> Floors for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=11'>Gen 50:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=37'>Jdg 6:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=3&verse=14'>Rth 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=23&verse=1'>1Sa 23:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=6'>2Sa 6:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=2'>Hos 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=24'>Joe 2:24</a><br/> Floor of Araunah bought by David for a place of sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=25'>2Sa 24:25</a><br/> Floor for, in barns<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=27'>2Ki 6:27</a>"}]}